data.description: Hard to find Greenville home on a corner lot. This place offers cathedral ceilings, newer plumbing, boiler furnace and hot water tank. 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, kitchen with dining area, and a nice big living room. Dry Michigan basement, fenced in rear yard for the small pets and a shed. There is a nice 3 season front area in the home for extra living space. 24 hour notice to show, hurry on this one!
